18#include "BarcodeFormat.h"
19#include "BitHacks.h"
20#include "ZXContainerAlgorithms.h"
21
22#include <algorithm>
23#include <iterator>
24#include <string>
25#include <sstream>
26#include <stdexcept>
27
28namespace ZXing {
29
30static const char* FORMAT_STR[] = {
31 "INVALID",
32 "AZTEC",
33 "CODABAR",
34 "CODE_39",
35 "CODE_93",
36 "CODE_128",
37 "DATA_MATRIX",
38 "EAN_8",
39 "EAN_13",
40 "ITF",
41 "MAXICODE",
42 "PDF_417",
43 "QR_CODE",
44 "RSS_14",
45 "RSS_EXPANDED",
46 "UPC_A",
47 "UPC_E",
48 "UPC_EAN_EXTENSION",
49};
50
51static_assert(Size(FORMAT_STR) == (int)BarcodeFormats::bitIndex(BarcodeFormat::_max) + 1,
52 "FORMAT_STR array is out of sync with BarcodeFormat");
53
54const char* ToString(BarcodeFormat format)
55{
56 return FORMAT_STR[BarcodeFormats::bitIndex(format)];
57}
58
59static std::string NormalizeFormatString(std::string str)
60{
61 std::transform(str.begin(), str.end(), str.begin(), [](char c) { return (char)std::tolower(c); });
62 str.erase(std::remove(str.begin(), str.end(), '_'), str.end());
63 return str;
64}
65
66static BarcodeFormat ParseFormatString(const std::string& str)
67{
68 auto pos = std::find_if(std::begin(FORMAT_STR), std::end(FORMAT_STR),
69 [str](auto fmt) { return NormalizeFormatString(fmt) == str; });
70 return pos == std::end(FORMAT_STR) ? BarcodeFormat::INVALID
71 : BarcodeFormat(1 << (std::distance(std::begin(FORMAT_STR), pos) - 1));
72}
73
74BarcodeFormat BarcodeFormatFromString(const std::string& str)
75{
76 return ParseFormatString(NormalizeFormatString(str));
77}
78
79BarcodeFormats BarcodeFormatsFromString(const std::string& str)
80{
81 auto normalized = NormalizeFormatString(str);
82 std::replace_if(
83 normalized.begin(), normalized.end(), [](char c) { return Contains(" ,", c); }, '|');
84 std::istringstream input(normalized);
85 BarcodeFormats res;
86 for (std::string token; std::getline(input, token, '|');) {
87 if(!token.empty()) {
88 auto bc = ParseFormatString(token);
89 if (bc == BarcodeFormat::INVALID)
90 throw std::invalid_argument("This is not a valid barcode format: " + token);
91 res |= bc;
92 }
93 }
94 return res;
95}
